*Description:

   +---------+         +---------+          +---------+
   | host    | ----->  | host    | ---> ... | host    |
   |  A1     | <-----  |  A2     | ... <--- |  An     |
   +---------+         +---------+          +---------+

This want to implement data transmission between two terminal hosts across
multiple hosts, where the connection method could be SSH, TCP, UDP, etc.

*Build
Use cmake to build, you can ref to these steps shown below:
    $ cd /path/to/src_dir
    $ mkdir build && cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ cmake --build .
